title: Amy Schumer & Chris Fischer | Coronavirus Antibody Test PSA
description:
Seth Meyers found a PSA that explains how coronavirus antibody tests work.

Then, Amy Schumer and Chris Fischer discuss their new cooking show on Food Network and talk about having to change their son's name a month after he was born.
